3#ifndef __NVKM_DISP_CONN_H__
4#define __NVKM_DISP_CONN_H__
5#include <engine/disp.h>
6
7#include <core/notify.h>
8#include <subdev/bios.h>
9#include <subdev/bios/conn.h>
10
11struct nvkm_connector {
12 struct nvkm_disp *disp;
13 int index;
14 struct nvbios_connE info;
15
16 struct nvkm_notify hpd;
17
18 struct list_head head;
19};
20
21int nvkm_connector_new(struct nvkm_disp *, int index, struct nvbios_connE *,
22 struct nvkm_connector **);
23void nvkm_connector_del(struct nvkm_connector **);
24void nvkm_connector_init(struct nvkm_connector *);
25void nvkm_connector_fini(struct nvkm_connector *);
26
27#define CONN_MSG(c,l,f,a...) do { \
28 struct nvkm_connector *_conn = (c); \
29 nvkm_##l(&_conn->disp->engine.subdev, "conn %02x:%02x%02x: "f"\n", \
30 _conn->index, _conn->info.location, _conn->info.type, ##a); \
31} while(0)
32#define CONN_ERR(c,f,a...) CONN_MSG((c), error, f, ##a)
33#define CONN_DBG(c,f,a...) CONN_MSG((c), debug, f, ##a)
34#define CONN_TRACE(c,f,a...) CONN_MSG((c), trace, f, ##a)
35#endif
